<h1 id=3D"ChannelsSD:PaymentInitiationCAPAPIV1toV2upgrade-ImpactedSystemSum=
mary"><span>Impacted System Summary</span></h1>
<p><br><strong>Impacted System Images</strong></p>
<p>=E2=AD=90 - Change&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp=
; =F0=9F=9F=A9 - New&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span c=
lass=3D"fabric-text-color-mark">=F0=9F=94=B5<span>&nbsp;</span></span>- Exi=
sting Implementation &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span>=
&nbsp;</span>:cross:<span>&nbsp;</span>- Decommission</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"relative-table wrapped confluenceTable" style=3D"width: 142=
9.58px;">
<thead class=3D"">
<tr class=3D"">
<th style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTh">=
<p>Cash Platform (<span class=3D"ui-provider gs b c d e f g h i j k l m n o=
 p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak">A014A6</span>)</p></th>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p>=E2=AD=90</p><p><br></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><strong>Payments MFE EXP API</strong></p><p>As part of Payment Initiatio=
n CAP API V2 changes, Channels is expected to submit(POST) the payment to V=
2 version of the API(<a href=3D"https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis=
/cap-prodsvcfulflmnt-pymntprocsng-pymntinit-v2" class=3D"external-link" rel=
=3D"nofollow">https://mesh.westpac.com.au/components/apis/cap-prodsvcfulflm=
nt-pymntprocsng-pymntinit-v2</a>) instead of V1 version. The changes will b=
e applicable in the Payments EXP postPayments endpoint(POST /payments) and =
the changes will be applicable in the "<strong><span style=3D"color: rgb(23=
,43,77);">postPaymentsController.helper.ts</span></strong>" EXP API compone=
nt to handle the following,</p>
<ul>
<li>EXP API request to CAP API request mapping, the code changes will be re=
quired in the <a href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projects/WDP/=
repos/galaxy-payment-microfrontend/browse/api/server/api/helpers/postPaymen=
tsController.helper.ts#84" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">generat=
ePaymentsRequestDataForCAP</a> function.</li>
<li>CAP API response to EXP API response mapping, the code changes will be =
required in the&nbsp;<a href=3D"https://bitbucket.srv.westpac.com.au/projec=
ts/WDP/repos/galaxy-payment-microfrontend/browse/api/server/api/helpers/pos=
tPaymentsController.helper.ts#12" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">=
transformPaymentsResponseFromCAPToUI</a> function.</li>
</ul></td>
</tr>
</thead>
</table>
</div>
<p><br></p>
