; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <s>description</s></p><p><br></p><p><strong>U=
pdate as of 24 Nov 2025:</strong><br>
 The Payments team confirmed that returning these attributes in the V2 resp=
onse requires significant effort. Since these attributes are not used by Ch=
annels for UI binding, V2 will exclude them. A quick review of Channels cod=
e supports this decision.</p></td>
